Name: Wibble
About the game: A challenging, silly, physics-based game. Wibble is an adorable squid-like alien struggling with Earth's gravity. Take control of Wibble's wobbly limbs. Maneuver through 30 increasingly difficult levels and face challenging obstacles. Movement is relative to the direction the body is facing. Place yourself in Wibble's shoes - er, tentacle appendages - and Become one with Wibble! Features Steam Leaderboard Compete against your friends and the world to get the best times! May the best Wibble win. Unlockables Unlock skins and props by progressing through the game. Customize your Wibble! Challenging Levels Journey through 30 unique levels with their own set of obstacles. Battle through guillotines, cannons, gravity and even cabbages. Master the controls. Help Wibble get to the other side!
